Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBMaterialUom

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBMaterialUom
public class JDBMaterialUom extends Object
JDBMaterialUom class is used to insert/update/delete records from the APP_MATERIAL_UOM table. This table contains a list of valid units of measure for a Material.
